description: This spatial coverage includes vector points and point labels that describe CORDIO and PRAREV in-water survey sites of the broader Djibouti Seascape. Each site has a set of fish and benthic community variables  distinguishing it from the surrounding sites. These characteristics include site name, functional group, total  fish biomass (kg/ha) and total fish abundance (individuals/ha).
name: Djibouti 2014 and 2016 Total  Fish Abundance (individuals/ha)
